                        <p>PCS Gas Natural = <span class="value">11.0 kWh/m¬≥</span> | PCS Propano = <span class="value">25.8 kWh/m¬≥</span> | PCS Butano = <span class="value">31.2 kWh/m¬≥</span></p>
                    </div>
