        <!-- C√ÅLCULO DE TUBER√çAS -->
        <section id="calculo-tuberias" class="section">
            <h2 class="section-title"><i class="fas fa-ruler"></i> 3. C√ÅLCULO HIDR√ÅULICO DE TUBER√çAS</h2>
            
            <div class="subsection">
                <h3 class="subsection-title"><i class="fas fa-water"></i> 3.1. Ecuaci√≥n de Renouard para Media Presi√≥n</h3>
                
                <div class="formula-container">
                    <div class="formula-title">Ecuaci√≥n general de Renouard</div>
                    <div class="formula">
                        $$P_1^2 - P_2^2 = 48.6 \times \delta \times L \times Q^{1.82} \times D^{-4.82}$$
                    </div>
                    <div class="formula-variables">
                        <div class="variable">
                            <div class="variable-name">P‚ÇÅ</div>
                            <div>Presi√≥n absoluta inicial (bar)</div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="variable">
                            <div class="variable-name">P‚ÇÇ</div>
                            <div>Presi√≥n absoluta final (bar)</div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="variable">
                            <div class="variable-name">Œ¥</div>
                            <div>Densidad relativa del gas (aire=1)</div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="variable">
                            <div class="variable-name">L</div>
                            <div>Longitud equivalente (m)</div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="variable">
                            <div class="variable-name">Q</div>
                            <div>Caudal de gas (m¬≥/h)</div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="variable">
                            <div class="variable-name">D</div>
                            <div>Di√°metro interior (mm)</div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="example">
                    <div class="example-title"><i class="fas fa-calculator"></i> Ejemplo de aplicaci√≥n</div>
                    <p>Calcular la ca√≠da de presi√≥n en un tramo de 30m de tuber√≠a de cobre 22x1 con caudal de 5 m¬≥/h de gas natural (Œ¥=0.62), presi√≥n inicial 20 mbar (0.02 bar absoluto = 1.013+0.02 bar):</p>
                    
                    <div class="formula-container">
                        <div class="formula">$$P_1 = 1.033\ bar\ (absoluto)$$</div>
                        <div class="formula">$$D = 22 - 2 \times 1 = 20\ mm$$</div>
                        <div class="formula">$$P_1^2 - P_2^2 = 48.6 \times 0.62 \times 30 \times 5^{1.82} \times 20^{-4.82}$$</div>
                        <div class="formula">$$P_1^2 - P_2^2 = 48.6 \times 0.62 \times 30 \times 19.7 \times 0.00000167$$</div>
                        <div class="formula">$$P_1^2 - P_2^2 = 0.0296$$</div>
                        <div class="formula">$$P_2 = \sqrt{1.033^2 - 0.0296} = \sqrt{1.067 - 0.0296} = \sqrt{1.0374} = 1.018\ bar$$</div>
                        <div class="formula">$$\Delta P = 1.033 - 1.018 = 0.015\ bar = 15\ mbar$$</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="subsection">
                <h3 class="subsection-title"><i class="fas fa-long-arrow-alt-right"></i> 3.2. Longitud Equivalente - Accesorios</h3>
                
                <div class="table-container">
                    <table class="data-table">
                        <thead>
                            <tr>
                                <th>Accesorio</th>
                                <th>Longitud Equivalente (m)</th>
                                <th>Di√°metro 15 mm</th>
                                <th>Di√°metro 22 mm</th>
                                <th>Di√°metro 28 mm</th>
                                <th>Di√°metro 35 mm</th>
                            </tr>
                        </thead>
                        <tbody>
                            <tr>
                                <td>Codo 90¬∞</td>
                                <td>0.5 - 0.8</td>
                                <td>0.5</td>
